@sanitysnoop Sorry dude, My ISP has a fair use policy that limits my upload and download total per month to 300GB. If i seed anymore my speed could be reduced to crap. 

I do normally seed for two weeks on every torrent but they sent an email recently saying that i had reached 280GB that month and that they could reduce my speed. 

The ISP is actually a pretty lenient one so if i change the situations not gonna be much better, especially considering its the only ISP in the area that is Fibre optic and others would cut my speed in half.
